      • logFeatureUpdate

        @WorkerThread
void logFeatureUpdate(Feature feature,
                                     byte[] rawData,
                                     Feature.Sample sample)
        Call when we have to log some data

        the rawData array can be null if we extract multiple feature data that are notify to the user in different moment. in that case the only in the first call we will have a rawData!=null

        Parameters:
        feature - feature that has updated
        rawData - raw data that used for update the feature
        sample - data extracted by the feature
